<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你待会儿，<delay8 />也要参加钓鱼大赛吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和我决胜负吧！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我是很想这么说，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是钓鱼大赛<delay8 />并不采用对战形式啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 />论气势我是不会输的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />钓鱼大赛的规则是，<delay8 />你钓到的鱼越多，<delay8 />
你能获得的积分就越高！<pageBreak />换句话说，<delay20 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管啥种类，<delay8 />钓得越多越好！<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很简单吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说到鱼，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生活在池塘或者沼地里的鱼，<delay8 />
会因为特有的腥味而被嫌弃。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，<delay8 />只有善于运用它的腥味来制作料理，<delay20 />
这样的料理<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才有它的闪光点啊。<10_4 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就看如何<delay8 />用心发明新菜谱了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />钓鱼大赛<delay8 />正在火热进行中呢！<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不参加吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想参加的话，<delay20 />
去广场找<colour id="3" />俞司廷<colour id="65535" />就行。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你问我参不参加钓鱼大赛？<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我感觉，<delay8 />今天不想钓鱼。<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的信条就是，<delay8 />
在自己想做的时候，<delay8 />做自己喜欢的事！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />我挺喜欢鱼的，<delay8 />
也不讨厌钓鱼。<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次有机会我会参加的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>